    public static interface DatagramWanEmulator.Scheduled
extends Comparable<DatagramWanEmulator.Scheduled>
    Interface for handling scheduled objects, that should be processed at a given time.
    The time is represented as the difference in ms, between the time this object is ready to be processed and midnight, 01.01.1970 UTC.

      • isReady

        boolean isReady(long timeNow)
        Check whether this object is ready to be processed.
        Parameters:
        timeNow - the current low-resolution system time in ms, which will be used to determine if this object is ready yet. It represents the difference between the current time and midnight, 01.01.1970 UTC.
        Returns:
        true, iff object is ready to be processed, false otherwise
